reviewText: The episodes on this DVD box set appear in other classic TV westerns DVD box sets. You would be better off getting the following two classic TV western dVD box sets: Classic TV Westerns 300 Episodes Essential TV Western 150 Episodes If you get the above two DVD box sets, then you will not have to get any of the others that appear on teh web site, because they are all basically smaller sets and have the same episodes that appear in the above mentioned two DVD bvox sets. Additonal Infromation: The 399 episodes set Classic TV Westerns 300 Episodes is a combination of the two following DVD box sets: Ultimate TV Westerns - 150 Episodes Western TV Classics 150 Episodes
